{"url": "https://book.douban.com/subject/1000162/", "id": "1000162", "title": "惊弦集", "cover": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/subject/l/public/s1354348.jpg", "base": "作者: 黄裳出版社:河北教育出版社副标题:没理由陶醉出版年:2004-01页数:260定价:16.00装帧:平装丛书: 世相丛书ISBN:9787543452633", "intro": "目录掌上的烟云杂文复兴灯下杂谈谜底一念之微谈“癖”“牛棚”与牛“作家”的进化文学家与数学家“这也是生活”妓院里的爱情鬼恋手掌好快刀“文责自负”如梦记打差别戏法月下老人的诗签长官意志弭谤诚则灵关于“游山玩水”《负暄录》关于《入蜀记》我的端砚博与约蒋子文及其他油焖笋音容宛在……黄裳，1919年生，山东益都人。曾从事记者、编辑、电影剧本编剧、戏曲编剧。20世纪40年代开始散文创作，并熟于版本目录之学。撰有《锦帆集》、《旧戏新谈》、《过去的足迹》、《榆下说书》、《银鱼集》、《翠墨集》、《黄裳论剧杂文》、《黄裳书话》等三十余种，辑有《黄裳文集》六卷。", "tags": ["黄裳", "散文随笔", "散文", "文学", "轻柔", "贰", "流行", "散文/隨筆/雜文"], "score": {"avg": " 6.2 ", "scroe_num": "30", "rating": ["3.3%", "23.3%", "66.7%", "6.7%", "0.0%"]}, "comments": [{"comment_id": "1595918061", "nick_name": "SydneyCarton", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/SydneyCarton/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1210604-80.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2018-12-28", "content": "<span class=\"short\">忆旧散文比杂文好得多。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "515010609", "nick_name": "白牙", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/holym/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2464745-1.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">快哉集 冯英子</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1112472138", "nick_name": "季米", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/1821514/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1821514-9.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2017-03-04", "content": "<span class=\"short\">黄裳的重编杂文集，和湖南那本篇目有别，这类文字写得一般，没啥特色，还是写人的几篇更值得一读。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1117186862", "nick_name": "齐物秋水", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/3790983/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3790983-100.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2016-12-05", "content": "<span class=\"short\">在杂文中，黄裳的神采消泯大半。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1107759796", "nick_name": "群山", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/16121581/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u16121581-400.jpg", "use_num": "1", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2016-11-18", "content": "<span class=\"short\">此书误植错讹处颇多，阅之犹如飞沙入目，难于卒章。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1222482658", "nick_name": "哥特的低叹", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/1513979/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1513979-262.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2017-07-31", "content": "<span class=\"short\">食之无味</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1265187387", "nick_name": "豆官", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/80768366/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u80768366-41.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2017-11-01", "content": "<span class=\"short\">四书用的统一书号？我看的何满子《将进酒》</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1107657538", "nick_name": "西鄙人", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/72430098/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u72430098-9.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2016-11-10", "content": "<span class=\"short\">黄裳先生杂文集，粗略翻过，不若《故人书简》有趣。所刺之人，多以作古，所讽之事，阴魂不散。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1122728452", "nick_name": "国王说谎", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/128123715/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u128123715-22.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2016-12-18", "content": "<span class=\"short\">”没有理由陶醉“</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1141649585", "nick_name": "Ari°", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/51256735/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u51256735-11.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2017-01-25", "content": "<span class=\"short\">四人帮出镜率极高... 读完才知道是86年编好的书..</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1113486064", "nick_name": "媳妇名叫贺妞妞", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/152904840/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u152904840-1.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2016-11-26", "content": "<span class=\"short\">《惊弦集》，黄裳老先生的一部社会随感和论剧杂文集，书中诸多触及时弊之语在今天看来依旧不合时宜，文字简洁明快，包容量大，遣词造句十分到位……</span>\n            "}], "reviews": [{"review_id": "1000971", "review_title": "細敍傷痕不喊痛", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/marshsu/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000068-16.jpg", "nick_name": "mars", "review_score": "allstar40 main-title-rating", "review_time": "2005-06-27 21:23:27", "review_content": "<div class=\"main-bd\">\n\n\n    \n  \n    \n\n    <div id=\"link-report\">\n      <div class=\"review-content clearfix\" data-author=\"mars\" data-url=\"https://book.douban.com/review/1000971/\" data-original=\"0\">\n        將黃裳先生的《驚弦集》大致讀完。說“大致”，因爲實際上有些篇章是略過的。<br><br>黃老先生這本雜文集，筆觸和我讀過的《黃裳書話》筆觸接近，但内容是集結1950-1994年間的心得雜文。不止談書，也談生活細瑣，談經歷、觀點。<br><br>此集若要當作“散文”來讀，用詞不夠優美，選字不夠精煉。<br>黃老循的是魯迅的脈，走的是雜文的路。<br><br>此書開篇“掌上的煙雲”和“雜文復興”便為自己的立場作了清楚的表述，沒有誤解的必要。雖然文句不飾美詞，内容卻栩栩如生。<br><br>觀點因爲與在下的人生經驗、時代背景和價值觀不同而未必全部認同，但敍事讀在心頭，點滴有深意。<br><br>黃老先生細敍過往傷痕而不喊痛，和其他人唏噓“十年浩劫”期間的苦痛血淚經歷筆觸大相庭徑。<br><br><br>節錄幾段：<br>“從1965年下半年開始，我就自覺地不大寫毛筆字了。現在想想也真有點古怪，當時的思想似乎確是有些’激進’，想想時至今日，寫字還要用毛筆和硯臺，即使客氣點不算做反動，落伍是無疑的了。<br>在這種思想指導之下，兩塊從廣東陸興到北京，又旅行到上海的石頭就被我放到房角的書架下面，以示不再動用。不料在一次頗爲徹底的抄家中，終于被發現了。因爲是從’隱蔽’的地方發現，就被懷疑為’金銀財寶’那樣的物事；後來又給同來的一個人看過，他驚呼道’這是端硯!’<br>這在當時確是使我吃了一驚。倒並非因爲被發現了’秘密的寶貝’；出乎意料的是，此時此地竟還有識得端硯的人物。我確是非常高興了，因爲連我自己也吃不准是真是假的兩塊石頭，終于得到了權威的鑑定。我收藏的是端硯，應是無可懷疑的了。”—1980年《我的端硯》<br><br><br>“我的一些藏書，在十年浩劫中被抄去以後，弄得七零八落、殘缺不全了。其中比較整齊的部分，存在圖書館裏，至今還不能發還。什麽原因？誰也説不清楚，總之是複雜得很，還是不去研究的好……<br>譬如’找得到什麽，就還你什麽，找不到就拉倒’。’還你錢！’這是什麽意思呢？我想了半天，終于不能懂。<br>譬如，’我又沒有抄你的家，你找我幹什麽？’這是千真萬確的。當年抄家的人，都好好的坐在別的什麽地方，一個都不在這裡。按理，也許應該去找’四人幫’，可惜又不知道他們住在哪裏，真是沒有法子想。……<br>這裡只是隨意摘取，雖然各有特色，但決不就是全部的精粹。但僅此數條，也足以悟出，我當然不被看作’失主’，’強盜’也不見了。但’贓物’卻在的。我必須扮演一個可憐的乞求者，恭順地’呈請發還’被搶去的自己的東西。什麽時候高興給就給一點，給多少也要看造化的高低。這是一種怎麽樣的情景呢？那是費盡心機也參不透的。”—1980年《負暄錄—打拳》<br><br><br>其他如“油燜筍”等生活細節的過程描述等，也是平鋪直述中冷嘲多於熱諷。這篇連流水賬都不算的文字，卻頗有太宰治的自嘲風味。<br><br>整本書讀起來帶點“無賴派”文風，但並不走到那麽極端。<br><br>可能是浩劫的“心有餘悸”吧，直接的口吻中黃老總是找到一個“恰當”的臺階給別人下，也是敦厚用心。<br><br>1919年山東益都出生的黃裳老先生現年應有86高齡，我很想找到他近期的作品閲讀呢。<br><br><br>原寫于2005年06月27日日記<br><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mars.blog-city.com/1360170.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://mars.blog-city.com/1360170.htm</a><br><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mars.blogbus.com/logs/2005/06/1290110.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://mars.blogbus.com/logs/2005/06/1290110.html</a><br>\n      </div>\n\n      \n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"main-author\">\n      \n  \n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n      \n  ", "use_num": "\n      有用 9\n  ", "nouse_num": "\n      没用 1\n  ", "review_share": "1", "review_reward": "", "review_comments": [{"comment_id": "1452", "nick_name": "阿北", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/ahbei/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000001-30.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-06-27 21:47:13", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">已经更新了。原来跟了席殊的错误。</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "1453", "nick_name": "mars", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/marshsu/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000068-16.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-06-27 21:49:34", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">多謝！</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "1459", "nick_name": "边之", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/bianzhi/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000161-1.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-06-27 23:04:01", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">《藏书家》里还见过他的文章，可惜今年出到第10期便停刊了。</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "1463", "nick_name": "mars", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/marshsu/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000068-16.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-06-28 11:04:16", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">謝謝邊之。至少還可以找到他今年的文字。\r<br>寫在《藏書家》裏，該還是說讀書心得吧？有特別印象深刻的觀點嗎？</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "1468", "nick_name": "边之", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/bianzhi/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000161-1.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-06-28 17:52:27", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">嘻嘻~誤會~剛才去看過，原來是每期有篇《來燕榭書跋》的連載，只在第二期裏有一篇“斷簡零篇室書摭憶”，末尾落款：1999年12月18日，與《來燕榭書跋》同一時間哦。</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "1472", "nick_name": "mars", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/marshsu/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000068-16.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-06-28 23:30:24", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">原來如此啊。沒關係。還是謝謝你！\r<br>《來燕榭書跋》我也沒看過、可以找來看看。</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "1481", "nick_name": "jing", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/1001700/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1001700-1.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-06-29 13:32:31", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">我买了黄裳文集，黄裳书话、旧戏新谈等著作。最喜欢他谈戏剧的文章，谈古籍版本的文章，就不太爱看了。可能也跟自己的喜好和修养有关吧。</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "1484", "nick_name": "阿北", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/ahbei/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000001-30.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-06-29 15:34:39", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">我手里有88年出的“彩色的花雨”，大学时糊里糊涂地买下了（定价1.6元）。薄薄的小册子。黄裳把京剧段子改成了一个个小故事。当时就觉得好看, 但不知道黄裳是谁：\r<br>\r<br><a href=\"https://www.douban.com/link2/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdouban.com%2Fsubject%2F1067974%2F\">http://douban.com/su<wbr></wbr>bject/1067974/</a> （封面不一样）</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "1485", "nick_name": "mars", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/marshsu/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000068-16.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-06-29 15:38:24", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">xiaojing, 我也喜歡他談戲曲。獨到精彩。\r<br>但其他的文字則屬於平實可掬，也好。\r<br>\r<br>阿北買到的彩色的花雨是黃裳説戲的書呢。我要找來看^_^真多謝！</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "1503", "nick_name": "徐江屏", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/holden/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000559-2.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-06-30 09:12:39", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">常能在《萬象》裏讀到黃先生的文章，每回讀總又落入悠遠的空茫裏。也不知道錯過了那來自於豐厚素養的隨意之作，對自己而言算不算是損失。畢竟那是生活的淬煉，學不來的。</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "1529", "nick_name": "mars", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/marshsu/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000068-16.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-07-01 00:59:11", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">遇見了便是緣份，每個人自有造化。他的我們得以分享，也就足夠幸福了，對嗎？</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "2617", "nick_name": "fivestone", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/fivestone/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1007091-1.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-08-04 22:04:36", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">诶，上了豆瓣才惊觉自己绝大多数书都是\"大致\"读完\r<br>连书评都不好意思写了</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "3233", "nick_name": "mars", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/marshsu/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000068-16.jpg", "comment_time": "2005-08-17 21:48:32", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">沒關係啊。不寫書評，便寫點感想也好。</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "75675", "nick_name": "好色乐之", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/1040075/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1040075-1.jpg", "comment_time": "2006-10-12 10:34:34", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">黄裳的散文不能算优美，杂文不能说精准犀利，幽默感也不够，但难得的是那种火气和真气，不为人左右，情感从不掩饰，爱、敬、钦佩、怜悯、可惜、蔑视，但没有憎恨，一直到老都不改，如此一切技巧上的不完美都可忽略了。\r<br>\r<br>他的书基本上是见一本收一本的，未必都看，放着也好。收有他的来燕榭读书记，来燕榭集外文钞，旧戏新谈，白门秋柳，珠还记幸，和这本惊弦集，新版珠还记幸尤其好看，图文都漂亮极了。\r<br>\r<br></p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "75680", "nick_name": "好色乐之", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/1040075/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1040075-1.jpg", "comment_time": "2006-10-12 10:39:39", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">另外我觉得黄裳最好的文章就是他写古籍收藏的那些，资料翔实，叙述清楚，细读很有益。其次是写人的，有真气，自抒己见。\r<br>\r<br>写戏的文章虽然更受人欢迎，但我觉得浅了点。</p>\n\n      "}, {"comment_id": "7970021", "nick_name": "群山", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/16121581/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u16121581-400.jpg", "comment_time": "2016-11-11 10:50:07", "content": "<p class=\"comment-text\">黄老此书给后辈读书人留下太多的悬疑抑或八卦，仅开篇《掌上风云》便至少有十个疑点可以追索，倘有心人对此能一一爬梳清楚，倒也不失为文坛掌故秘辛。</p>\n\n      "}]}]}